metadata.description: Transcript of radio message relayed by the Commanding General of the U.S. Army Forces in the Far East (USAFFE) containing a message from President Franklin D. Roosevelt for President Manuel L. Quezon promising the fulfilment of the United States' obligation to protect the Philippines "to the last extremity."
